attributes.Long form description: The student changes the battery and sd card of the GoPro, turns it on and then turns it off, mounts the GoPro into a belt, changes it into a tripod, and then changes it into a handheld grip, and finally removes the GoPro from the handheld grip, and puts all the parts separately.

attributes.Transcription: Hello, and thank you for agreeing to take part in the study.
In front of you, you'll see a GoPro action camera we'll be using it for this task.
First can you please change the battery in the GoPro.

To open the battery compartment, please slide the metal slit on the right compartment downwards.
On the lower part of the compartment, you will see a little hole in the middle please slide that down.
Please hold it, and use it to open the door.
